reviews.text:
Surplus shopping arcade nearby to MOSTown and Ma On Shan Plaza. You'll find a couple eateries but mostly language, music and other tutorial centres, interior designers, dentists, realtors convenient shop and access to residential housing above the commercial space. 

In the end, this is targeted and functional commercial space, a place for area residents, not really a place for those looking for typical shopping. For that just go to MOSTown or even over to Sha Tin to New Town Plaza instead.
self pick up lockers for goods delivery are installed in the shopping center
Good
